GliderSK (Garmin ConnectIQ) App
===============================
Privacy information

GliderSK does not collect and transmit any data to any 3rd-party, save for the
Activity files you record and upload to Garmin (Connect) when synchronizing
your device.

The permissions required by GliderSK are:
 - "Sensor" permission:
   for acceleration data
 - "Positioning" permission:
   for location, elevation and speed data
 - "Fit" permission:
   for recording your Activity (to FIT file)
 - "FitContributor" permission:
   to add vertical speed, rate of turn and acceleration data in your
   recorder Activity (FIT file)
 - "Communications" permission:
   to import data from the web into your destinations memory
   (see the Storage Data section in the USAGE file)
